19:T717,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Does the price include implementation, or just the plan?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"The Starter and Full Roadmap engagements cover the planning phase — the strategy, the workflow analysis, the AI Task Canvases, and the implementation roadmap. They do not include the development and deployment of AI systems. Implementation is a separate engagement, scoped and priced based on the specific use cases identified in the plan."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I pay in Qatari riyals?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The listed prices are in USD for international consistency. QAR equivalent at current exchange rates: Starter is approximately QAR 3,630 and Full Roadmap is approximately QAR 9,085."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is there a payment plan available?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"For the Full Roadmap engagement, a split payment arrangement — 50% at the start of the engagement and 50% on delivery of the completed implementation plan — is available."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you work with businesses outside Qatar?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. The AI Navigator framework has been applied to businesses across the GCC and internationally. The data sovereignty and PDPPL compliance elements adjust accordingly for businesses operating under different regulatory frameworks."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can a group of businesses go through the framework together?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. A cohort format — where six to ten businesses from similar sectors go through Chapters 1 to 6 together in group sessions — is available at a lower per-business cost. Contact us to discuss cohort pricing."}}]}f:[["$","$L2",null,{"id":"faq-schema","type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$19"}}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrap","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"breadcrumb","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"/","children":"Home"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":" › "}],["$","a",null,{"href":"/resources/","children":"Resources"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":"true","children":" › "}],["$","span",null,{"children":"How Much Does AI Consulting Cost in Qatar?"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"children":"How Much Does AI Consulting Cost in Qatar?"}],[["$","p","0",{"children":"The honest answer is: it depends enormously on what you are actually buying."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"AI consulting in Qatar ranges from a few thousand riyals for a one-day workshop with no deliverables, to hundreds of thousands for a multi-year enterprise transformation programme with a global firm. Most business owners asking this question are somewhere in the middle — they want to make a real start with AI, they want structured guidance, and they want to know what a fair price looks like for the scope of work they need."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"This page breaks down the cost landscape honestly. It explains what drives price up or down, what different types of AI consulting actually include, and what the AI Navigator engagement costs at each tier."}]],["$","div",null,{"className":"cta-box","style":{"margin":"32px 0"},"children":["$","$L1a",null,{"href":"/","location":"resource_mid_ai-consulting-cost-qatar"}]}],[["$","section","0",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Why AI Consulting Prices Vary So Widely"}],"$undefined",[["$","p","0",{"children":"Four factors determine what any AI consulting engagement costs. Scope of work — there is a fundamental difference between an engagement that produces a written strategy and one that builds and deploys working AI systems. Methodology depth — a structured engagement that produces documented outputs at each stage takes more time than a set of slides with recommendations. Seniority and expertise — the GCC market currently has a shortage of genuine AI expertise and a surplus of generalists. Duration and relationship model — a one-off project engagement costs less than a retainer model."}]]]}],"$L1b","$L1c","$L1d"],"$L1e","$L1f","$undefined","$L20","$L21"]}]]
22:I[6203,["619","static/chunks/619-ba102abea3e3d0e4.js","549","static/chunks/app/(site)/resources/%5Bslug%5D/page-82b918b41d4220bf.js"],"default"]
1b:["$","section","1",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"The Three Types of AI Consulting You Can Buy in Qatar"}],"$undefined",[["$","p","0",{"children":"<strong>Type 1 — Vendor-led AI consulting:</strong> Technology vendors offer consulting as part of a sale. The advice is genuine in intent but structurally biased toward the vendor's product."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"<strong>Type 2 — Enterprise AI consulting:</strong> Global management consulting firms offer AI strategy and transformation programmes. Quality is generally high. Cost reflects it — typically starting at QAR 150,000 to QAR 500,000 for a strategy engagement. For an SME with 10 to 200 employees, this is structurally mismatched."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"<strong>Type 3 — SME-focused AI advisory:</strong> A structured engagement designed specifically for businesses that do not have enterprise budgets. This is where the AI Navigator framework sits."}]]]}]
1c:["$","section","2",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"What the AI Navigator Engagement Costs"}],"$undefined",[["$","p","0",{"children":"<strong>Starter Engagement — Teams Under 10:</strong> $997 (approximately QAR 3,630). Two structured working sessions over two weeks. Covers Chapters 1–6 of the AI Navigator framework. Written deliverables: Strategic Vision Canvas, Starting Point Assessment, Strategy Selection Decision, Prioritised Workflow List, AI Potential Ranked Task List. Also includes a free copy of The AI Roadmap and tool recommendations."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"<strong>Full Roadmap Engagement — Teams of 10 and Above:</strong> $2,497 (approximately QAR 9,085). Four structured working sessions over four weeks covering the complete AI Navigator framework. Includes everything in the Starter engagement, plus AI Task Canvas documents, Optimised Process Maps, Tool Requirements Profile, and a complete Phased Implementation Plan."}],["$","p","2",{"children":"<strong>Enterprise and Custom Engagements:</strong> For larger businesses or organisations with complex data sovereignty requirements under Qatar's PDPPL framework. Pricing reflects the specific scope and is discussed during a discovery call."}]]]}]
1d:["$","section","3",{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Is the Investment Worth It?"}],"$undefined",[["$","p","0",{"children":"The relevant comparison is not consulting fee versus zero. It is consulting fee versus the cost of the alternative. The average SME in Qatar that runs AI experiments without a structured framework spends QAR 15,000 to QAR 50,000 on tool subscriptions, developer time, and failed pilots in the first year before arriving at conclusions a planning engagement would have produced in 30 days."}],["$","p","1",{"children":"If an AI implementation that reduces your team's routine workload by 40% saves 20 hours of staff time per week, the annual value at a conservative QAR 50 per hour is QAR 52,000. The plan that produces that implementation costs QAR 9,085. That is a 5.7x return before implementation has even begun."}]]]}]
1e:["$","section",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Frequently Asked Questions"}],["$","$L22",null,{"faqs":[{"q":"Does the price include implementation, or just the plan?","a":"The Starter and Full Roadmap engagements cover the planning phase — the strategy, the workflow analysis, the AI Task Canvases, and the implementation roadmap. They do not include the development and deployment of AI systems. Implementation is a separate engagement, scoped and priced based on the specific use cases identified in the plan."},{"q":"Can I pay in Qatari riyals?","a":"Yes. The listed prices are in USD for international consistency. QAR equivalent at current exchange rates: Starter is approximately QAR 3,630 and Full Roadmap is approximately QAR 9,085."},{"q":"Is there a payment plan available?","a":"For the Full Roadmap engagement, a split payment arrangement — 50% at the start of the engagement and 50% on delivery of the completed implementation plan — is available."},{"q":"Do you work with businesses outside Qatar?","a":"Yes. The AI Navigator framework has been applied to businesses across the GCC and internationally. The data sovereignty and PDPPL compliance elements adjust accordingly for businesses operating under different regulatory frameworks."},{"q":"Can a group of businesses go through the framework together?","a":"Yes. A cohort format — where six to ten businesses from similar sectors go through Chapters 1 to 6 together in group sessions — is available at a lower per-business cost. Contact us to discuss cohort pricing."}]}]]}]
1f:["$","div",null,{"className":"cta-box","children":[["$","h2",null,{"style":{"marginTop":0},"children":"Ready to assess your AI readiness?"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"The AI Readiness Assessment evaluates your business across five dimensions — workflow type, decision complexity, data availability, process volume, and team size — and gives you a personalised score with specific recommended next steps. It takes three minutes."}],["$","$L1a",null,{"href":"/","location":"resource_bottom_ai-consulting-cost-qatar"}]]}]
20:["$","div",null,{"className":"author-bio","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Allan Sendagi"}]," is the author of ",["$","em",null,{"children":"The AI Roadmap"}]," and founder of SafeHaven AI. He works with SMEs across Qatar and the GCC to build structured AI implementation plans using the AI Navigator framework."]}],["$","p",null,{"style":{"marginTop":8},"children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"/","style":{"color":"var(--brand)","fontWeight":600},"children":"Take the free AI Readiness Assessment"}]," · ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://calendly.com/allan-safehavenai/30min","style":{"color":"var(--brand)","fontWeight":600},"children":"Book a discovery call"}]]}]]}]
